If you do not receive your notice by April 7, 2021, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Notice Was Returned To USCIS Because The Post Office Could Not Deliver It
body: On March 19, 2021, the Post Office returned a notice we sent you for your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190071999, because they could not deliver it. This could have a serious effect on your case. Please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice immediately. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
